	<div class="node-inner">
    
    
    		    
    
  	<div class="content">
  	  <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><h1>Living Justice, Loving Mercy, Serving Christ</h1>
<p>Compelled by God’s deep passion for justice &amp; mercy, we join communities around the world to renew hope, reconcile lives, and restore creation.<a name="where" id="where"></a></p>
</div></div></div>  	</div>
  	
      	
